Class DelegatingFacesContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.faces.context.FacesContext
      • org.jboss.seam.jsf.DelegatingFacesContext

  • public class DelegatingFacesContext
extends javax.faces.context.FacesContext
    Implementation of FacesContext that delegates all calls. Further, it exposes setCurrentInstance(FacesContext) as a public method

    Pete Muir
